Package: autograder
Title: Automated R Function Testing and Grading
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Agub", "Reijel", 
           email = "rcagub@up.edu.ph", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    An automated grading system for R programming assignments. Securely fetches 
    test cases from a remote repository and compares student implementations 
    against reference solutions. Supports weighted scoring, hidden tests, type 
    checking, and tolerance-based comparisons. Designed for educational use in 
    statistics and data science courses with security features to protect test 
    cases and instructor solutions.
